WEBVTT

00:04.720 --> 00:06.040
<i>That Lydia bitch Quigley.</i>

00:06.120 --> 00:07.480
<i>She's trying to keep me down.</i>

00:07.560 --> 00:09.720
<i>That woman is pure menace.</i>

00:09.800 --> 00:11.520
Sometimes...

00:11.600 --> 00:13.200
<i>God just fills your glass.</i>

00:15.440 --> 00:17.000
<i>What's your price</i>
<i>so I may have her?</i>

00:17.120 --> 00:18.440
<i>I'll be taking sealed bids</i>

00:18.480 --> 00:19.840
<i>for Lucy's virginity</i>

00:19.960 --> 00:21.120
as I did for Charlotte,

00:21.240 --> 00:23.600
<i>my older daughter.</i>

00:23.640 --> 00:26.120
<i>...one of the brightest stars</i>
<i>in London's firmament.</i>

00:27.800 --> 00:28.800
Charlotte?

00:28.840 --> 00:30.840
Charlotte, you infernal whore!

00:30.960 --> 00:32.920
‐I want Lucy.
‐Lucy is exceptional.

00:33.040 --> 00:34.920
You may not ever refuse me.

00:35.040 --> 00:36.040
No!

00:39.360 --> 00:41.480
<i>It's my murder now.</i>

00:41.560 --> 00:45.040
<i>The beast requires</i>
<i>feeding again.</i>

00:45.120 --> 00:48.080
<i>The hounds are coming,</i>
<i>vixen.</i>

00:48.120 --> 00:50.560
To catch a beast,
you must have bait.

00:50.680 --> 00:52.360
<i>If I knew</i>
<i>the nature of the beast,</i>

00:52.440 --> 00:54.480
how much better
I could nourish it.

00:55.440 --> 00:57.920
<i>If it is you,</i>

00:58.040 --> 00:59.320
who were they?

01:06.560 --> 01:08.640
<i>My mother was sold age 10.</i>

01:08.720 --> 01:09.840
<i>Lydia Quigley</i>

01:09.920 --> 01:11.280
<i>put her to work as a whore.</i>

01:11.360 --> 01:12.480
Charlotte!

01:12.560 --> 01:15.080
<i>Fate has put me</i>
<i>in her house,</i>

01:15.120 --> 01:16.840
and I will bring her down.

